comments: While defending on the perimeter, Poole (GSW) initiates contact with Lowry (MIA) off ball that dislodges him from his position.
Wiggins (GSW) makes contact to Butler's (MIA) body and affects his driving shot attempt.
Vincent (MIA) and Curry (GSW) both meet at the same point as Curry (GSW) is dribbling the ball into the front court. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Wiggins (GSW) establishes himself in Vincent's (MIA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.

Butler (MIA) is called for contact with Curry (GSW) on his jump shot. The call was overturned pursuant to a coach's challenge as Butler made contact to the ball and high-five contact with Curry's hand after the shot was released. The ball is awarded to MIA, who had imminent possession at the point of interruption.
Green (GSW) legally contests Vincent's (MIA) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Looney (GSW) establishes himself in Robinson's (MIA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Lowry (MIA) and Wiggins's (GSW) engage and disengage while rebounding.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Wiggins's (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Adebayo (MIA) extends his arm forward and initiates contact to Wiggins' (GSW) head and affects his ability to rebound.
Green (GSW) makes contact with the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Curry (GSW) and Vincent (MIA) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Poole (GSW) throws an errant pass and it goes out of bounds.
